===Etymology===
From {{etyl|fr}} {{term|pyramide||lang=fr}} ← {{etyl|fro}} {{term|piramide||lang=fro}} ← {{etyl|la}} {{term|pyramis||lang=la}} ← {{etyl|grc}} {{term|sc=polytonic|πυραμίς||tr=pyramis}}, from Ancient Egyptian ''pimar'' "pyramid".
:The Ancient Egyptian word for pyramid is {{tø|egy|mr|sc=Egyp}}.

